title: National Archives Confirms Trump Had Classified Material at Mar-a-Lago - The Wall Street Journal
content:
1. National Archives Confirms Trump Had Classified Material at Mar-a-Lago  The Wall Street Journal
  2. National Archives acknowledges classified documents were found in boxes at Mar-a-Lago after Trump left office  CNN
  3. Material Recovered From Trump by Archives Included Classified Information  The New York Times
  4. Many nations have more accountable government than the U.S. | Opinion  Deseret News

description: Former President Donald Trump had classified government records at his Florida residence, the National Archives informed a congressional panel, saying it was in communication with the Justice Department on the matter.
